                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">战争是人性的解剖课。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="513143533">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-513143533" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-513143533" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="513143533">有用</a>
